start benzene

memory 2000 mb

geometry units angstroms
  C1     0.000     1.400     0.000
  C2     1.213     0.700     0.000
  C3     1.213    -0.700     0.000 
  C4     0.000    -1.400     0.000
  C5    -1.213    -0.700     0.000
  C6    -1.213     0.700     0.000
  H1     0.000     2.486     0.000
  H2     2.153     1.243     0.000
  H3     2.153    -1.243     0.000
  H4     0.000    -2.486     0.000
  H5    -2.153    -1.243     0.000
  H6    -2.153     1.243     0.000
end

basis
  C library 6-31G
  H library 6-31G
end

dft
  mult 1 
  xc b3lyp
  maxiter 100
  print low
end

task dft

